{"id":"812042016846430208","type":"text","timestamp":1774423615,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/812042016846430208","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://seraphina-aureline.tumblr.com/post/811684625315512320/its-me-im-trans-woman\">seraphina-aureline</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/biblicallyaccurateromina/811453375817318400\">biblicallyaccurateromina</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/biblicallyaccurateromina/811440499700514816\">biblicallyaccurateromina</a>:</p><blockquote><p>“I turned out fine,” she says, staring so far off into space that you can see andromeda reflected in her eyes</p></blockquote><p>A trans woman will say “I’ve made peace with it” while clutching a stuffed animal so tightly that it begins to come apart at the seams </p></blockquote><p>it&rsquo;s me, I&rsquo;m &ldquo;trans woman&rdquo;&hellip;&hellip;.. &gt;.&lt;</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"biblicallyaccurateromina"},"post":{"id":"811440499700514816"}},{"blog":{"name":"biblicallyaccurateromina"},"post":{"id":"811453375817318400"}},{"blog":{"name":"seraphina-aureline"},"post":{"id":"811684625315512320"}}],"baseline_notes":7919,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}